data.title: Dominique Hourani
data.meta_description: Posts about Dominique Hourani written by lebanesecelebritynews
data.text:
Dominique Hourani posted the above photo of her on Instagram while she attended the launching of Al Fardan Jewellery in Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates.

Along the pic she wrote, ” During the opening of Al Fardan Jewelry in Abu Dhabi @saiidkobeisyofficial #tods #bag #pink #peach #evening_dress #haute_couture #happy #fashion #fashionista #uae #fancy #event #opening #red_carpet #class #glamour #designer #rolex @alfardanjwlry #alfardan.”

The 34-year-old singer looked gorgeous in a light pink sheer dress designed by Saiid Kobeisy that showed off her amazing curves.

Wow– she looks like a princess in pink!

Dominique Hourani shared the above photo of her on Instagram while she attended a fashion event at Burj Al Arab, in United Arab Emirates.

Along the pic she wrote, “From yesterday ‘s big fashion event at #burj_al_arab Let your cloth speaks about your silence @louisvuitton @amroladiessalon @famousspa #hair_style #louisvuitton #bag #dominiqueh #fashion #arabian #artist #singer #star #actress #songs #haute_couture #look #sexy #lebanon #uae #happy #girly #fashionista Dress by @innocent_touch.”

The 34-year-old Lebanese singer looked gorgeous in a dark blue/white striped long sleeved dress along with adorable gladiator bronze heels.

Aww– those heels… She’s such a fashionista! What do you think of her outfit?

Dominique Hourani shared the above photo of her on Instagram with her friend, the International singer/actress/model Paris Hilton.

Along the pic she wrote, “I love this energy full girl @parishilton #star #fashionistas #dj #famous #celebrity #friend #dominiqueh #fashion #arabian #artist #singer #star #actress #songs #look #sexy #lebanon #uae #happy #girly #fashionista.”

The 34-year-old Lebanese singer looked beautiful in blue jeans along with a blue colorful top.

Aww– what a wonderful gathering!

Wow– she looks amazing!

Dominique Hourani posted the above photo of her on Instagram while she was trying on a beautiful wedding dress for what it looks like a new photo shoot session.

Along the pic she wrote, “Do you think this is my bride’s maid? #dominiqueh #wedding @manalajaj.”

The Lebanese singer looked gorgeous in a white wedding dress designed by Manal Ajaj.

Aww– we would’ve liked to see her get married!

Dominique Hourani shared the above photo of her on Instagram while she attended her friend art exhibition at The Dubai Mall, in United Arab Emirates.

Along the pic she wrote, “Had a great time with my great #painter #friend #Loma @loumarabah #chanel #purse Love those #paintings .this art is just so #inspiring #dominiqueh #star #artist #singer #red_hair #chanel #fashion #art #painting thanks to @1001abayas for my nice #top at The Dubai Mall And Burj Khalifa Fountain.”

The 34-year-old Lebanese singer looked beautiful in grey leggings along with a grey floral poncho shirt and a grey purse by Chanel.

Dominique Hourani covered this month issue of Insight magazine, as she was named one of the most successful, sexy and thriving mom of the year 2015.

On the cover the singer wrote, “Happy #mother’s month to all #sweet #angels in the world #cover #magazine #Love my #baby #girl #romantic #mother #manalajaj @manalajaj #dress #magazine #cover_girl #insight #motherhood #child #star #love #romance #beauty #beautiful #fashionista #mom #baby #uae #emirates #dubai #saudi.”

The 34-year-old singer looked gorgeous in a white dress designed by Manal Ajaj that matched the outfit of her look alike daughter, Delara.

Aww–They look so adorable!

Dominique Hourani shared the above teaser photo of her on Instagram from her new music video for the song “Ah Menak” that will be released tomorrow.

Along the pic she wrote, “From my #video #ahmenak coming out tomorrow . Watch and Subscribe to Dominique’s channel on YouTube http://www.youtube.com/DominiqueHourani #dominiqueh #star #singer #video #car #sexy #lady #arabian #songs.”

The Lebanese singer looked beautiful in a black and gold top as she was fixing a yellow car. Wow!

We can’t wait to see the video clip!

Aww– like mother, like daughter indeed!

Dominique Hourani shared the above photo of her on Instagram while she was having a lovely fun day with her look alike daughter, Delara.

The 34-year-old Lebanese singer looked gorgeous in a white maxi skirt along with a white shirt, white purse and an adorable head band.

They look like angels! We love the look!

And she looks fabulous!

Dominique Hourani shared the above photo of her on Instagram while she was shooting her new upcoming video clip for the song “Al Silk Daribni”, in India.

The 34-year-old singer looked dazzling in several colorful outfits by Jupon Line. We’re loving the Indian look on her!

We can’t wait to see the music video that will be released soon!

What a sexy dress!

Dominique Hourani posted the above photo of her on Instagram while she was hosting a wedding performance in Dubai, United Arab Emirates.

The 34-year-old singer looked stunning in an aqua strapless dress with a slit designed by Saiid Kobeisy, along with adorable golden heels and accessories.

We can’t get enough of her hotness these days!
